# AI-Assisted Restaurant System

A Python-based desktop application developed for restaurant staff to manage orders efficiently and receive AI-assisted product recommendations during the ordering process.

## Overview
The system helps restaurant personnel create orders, calculate total prices automatically, and receive product suggestions based on previously selected items using association logic.

## Technologies
- Python
- Tkinter
- Basic AI (association-based recommendation)
- Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)

## Features
- Order management interface for staff
- Menu display
- Dynamic price calculation
- AI-based product recommendations
- Simple and user-friendly GUI

## How to Run
```bash
python main.py
